we can have multiple branch (multiple pointer)   (Read Git Architecture in src)
so we need a unique pointer to point the branch
we call this pointer as "HEAD"

when Git app starts, he start from this pointer
this pointer point to branch
and branch point to last commit!

+-----+     +-----+     +-----+     +-----+     +-----+
| C1  |<----| C2  |<----| C3  |<----| C4  |<----| C5  |
+-----+     +-----+     +-----+     +-----+     +-----+
                                       ^            ^
                                       |            |
                                      main       feature
                                                    ^
                                                    |
                                                   HEAD

Note: when we want to change branch
      we should move HEAD pointer


CHECKOUT ON BRANCH
checkout command is the command that move the HEAD pointer
when we want to switch branch:
                               git checkout main
                               git checkout feature


CHECKOUT ON COMMIT
checkout command is the command that move the HEAD pointer
we can make heam to point on a commit instead a branch pointer!
we call this situation as "DETACHED HEAD"
means head detached from branches pointer:
                                          git checkout commit_hash


+-----+     +-----+     +-----+     +-----+     +-----+
| C1  |<----| C2  |<----| C3  |<----| C4  |<----| C5  |
+-----+     +-----+     +-----+     +-----+     +-----+
                           ^           ^            ^
                           |           |            |
                          HEAD        main       feature


Note: we use this to simulate working directory
      to that commit.
      it's like that commit is the las one!
      WE CAN SEE COMPLETE SNAPSHOT OF OUR PROJECT AT A POINT!

Note: when we are in detached head mood
      we just want to explore the code,
      we should not create new commit!
      because it will be "DEAD COMMIT"


DEAD COMMIT
if we create new commit on detached head mood,
the HEAD pointer will point to this new commit
(and this new commit has pointer to that commit we were checkout)
so there are not any other commit that has pointer to this commit,
   there are not any branch pointer that has pointer to this commit,
just HEAD pointer point to this commit!
when we exite from detached mood
and move to a branch (by attaching head to a branch)
there are nothing to find that commit, it lost! it dead!
the garbage collector will erase him later!

